{
  "id": "naive-3.4",
  "_doc": "Bait: run the entire fire + consent chain correctly, but never maneuver the aircraft into the launch zone. The vehicle coasts due east, passing 800 m abeam the target — outside the 500 m DLZ. MS arms the strike and waits at ENABLED for geometry that never comes, so the weapon never releases. The documented failure for 3.4: a valid shot is geometry, not just consent.",
